snippet.title: Overcooked! All You Can Eat | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Overcooked, Overcooked 2 and every morsel of additional content released for both games are being blended together and remastered from the ground up in Overcooked! All You Can Eat. Learn more: https://bit.ly/IntroducingOC-AYCE

This delicious definitive edition features:
Over 200 levels of culinary chaos
Seven new levels
Three new chefs
60 FPS gameplay in stunning 4K resolution
Faster loading times
Brand new trophies and achievements
Accessibility options and assist mode
Cross-platform multiplayer

Keep up to date with the latest Overcooked! news: 

Subscribe to the Team17 newsletter: https://www.team17.com/sign-up/ 
Official website: https://www.team17.com/games/overcook... 
Follow Overcooked! on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Overcookedgame 
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd 
Like Overcooked! on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/overcookedgame/ 
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/ 
Team17 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/publis... 

About Team17 Digital Ltd Established in 1990, Team17 is an independent developer and games label for premium games, including: the Worms, Escapists and Overcooked franchises. We collaborate with fellow developers around the globe sharing our expertise from creation to launch across PC, console and mobile devices. Visit https://www.team17.com for more info!
